Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.38,0:00:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know there's an awesome\Ntreasure at the end of this sea?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.61,0:00:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And whoever gets it can be King\Nof the Pirates! Isn't that exciting?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.18,0:00:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unheard-of adventures are waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.39,0:00:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bon voyage! Let that shred of courage grow
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.26,0:00:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I caught a glimpse of\Nthe tail end to the future
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.90,0:00:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The horizons everyone\Ndreamed of were separate at first
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.68,0:01:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but now they can be seen\Nthrough a single telescope
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.82,0:01:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A bitter compass of destiny\Nis leading your heart astray
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.16,0:01:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so turn the wheel in the other direction!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.06,0:01:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bon voyage!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.13,0:01:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Toss aside your bonds and your past
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.37,0:01:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can surely smile despite that
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.38,0:01:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tears shed trying to achieve\Nyour dreams aren't for naught
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.86,0:01:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Precious in my life
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.26,0:01:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I caught a glimpse of\Nthe tail end to the future
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.81,0:02:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God Eneru and Luffy finally\Nclashed on the Ark Maxim.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.11,0:02:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell... are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.79,0:02:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.12,0:02:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a pirate and a rubber person.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.79,0:02:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rubber?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.46,0:02:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lightning has no effect\Nwhatsoever on a rubber person.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.13,0:02:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Strong as Eneru is, he felt threatened by Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.13,0:02:24.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grom... Puddling!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.52,0:02:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum... Battle-Axe!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.53,0:03:01.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As the battle intensified,\Nthe golden Ark Maxim finally took off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.18,0:03:11.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The circuit to this ark's ultimate feature\Nis already open and functioning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.52,0:03:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Its name is Deathpiea.\NIt's despair, the savior of this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.87,0:03:34.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think it's okay for a\Ngod to destroy everything?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.21,0:03:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum... Bazooka!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.58,0:03:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.58,0:03:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Rifle!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.20,0:04:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Luffy Falls!\NGod's Judgment and Nami's Wish!!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.26,0:04:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh! The ship is leaving the Vearth!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.60,0:04:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's flying! What should we do?!\NThe ship's gonna fly away!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.60,0:04:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did it! You did it!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.27,0:04:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You defeated Eneru!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.61,0:04:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But the ship is... the ship is flying away!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.99,0:05:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me...! Is he still getting up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.26,0:05:03.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.26,0:05:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Is that all you've got?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.60,0:05:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once you're gone, the world will be mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.28,0:05:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once again, everyone will fear me,\Nworship me, and revere me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.32,0:05:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My world!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.32,0:05:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vermin like you are no match for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.66,0:05:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To me... nothing is impossible!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.33,0:05:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the Almighty God!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.17,0:05:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.84,0:05:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! Something is floating\Nin the sky above Upper Yard!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.05,0:05:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A... A ship?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.72,0:06:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be! A flying ship...\NI've never heard of such a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.66,0:06:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that ship's what caused\Nthe sky to become dark?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.66,0:06:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God is on that ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.33,0:06:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.00,0:06:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of here, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.84,0:06:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Board the ships!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.71,0:06:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lots of ships are leaving Angel Island!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.72,0:06:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What on earth is going on?\NThose dark clouds... What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.22,0:06:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? Someone is coming this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.39,0:06:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahoy! Shandians!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.39,0:06:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should immediately\Nprepare your ships as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.40,0:06:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This nation is lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.07,0:06:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.40,0:06:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Escape!\N--To the Blue Sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.74,0:06:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T... To the Blue Sea?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.71,0:07:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.72,0:07:07.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God... Eneru...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.73,0:07:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Feast your eyes, rubber person...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.40,0:07:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...on the falling island's despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.41,0:07:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This will be the end of the sky island.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.41,0:07:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The lives of the angels will be terminated.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.41,0:07:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one can stop it any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.45,0:07:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course... that includes you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.78,0:07:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Stop it!!\N--Grom...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.79,0:07:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--The golden wall...!\N--How dare...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.12,0:07:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Puddling!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.46,0:07:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow! Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.46,0:07:50.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He melted it using the electric heat!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.63,0:07:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit, it burns!! Ahh!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.47,0:07:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.80,0:08:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't come off! Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.41,0:08:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rubber person from the Blue Sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.41,0:08:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I don't have to fight you, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.45,0:08:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this off! You bastard!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.45,0:08:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, I couldn't stand taking\Na hit while fighting you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.46,0:08:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.12,0:08:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...why don't we part here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.79,0:08:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In honor of the good fight\Nyou put up, I'll give you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.80,0:08:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...this gold!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.19,0:08:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.53,0:09:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once I confine you, the world\Nwill be mine, just as it was before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.80,0:09:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There will be no one in\Nthe world who can defeat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.47,0:09:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"In the world"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.48,0:09:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you stupid or what?\NThere are lots who can!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.85,0:09:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the Blue Sea, there're\Ntons of monstrous fighters!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.35,0:09:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone like you is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.19,0:09:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are a talkative brat, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.86,0:09:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fall! Together with the sky island!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.87,0:09:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone like you is...!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.37,0:09:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.54,0:09:41.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.88,0:09:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.75,0:09:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.42,0:09:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Luffy, Horsey-Bird! Luffy's falling!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.26,0:10:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's... Aisa! Pierre!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.59,0:10:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's who it was...\Nthat sly voice I've been hearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.93,0:10:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fight me!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.27,0:10:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! We're coming to save you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.28,0:10:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How annoying! You're wasting your time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.98,0:10:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aisa! Pierre! Watch out! Dodge it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.98,0:10:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eneru!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.66,0:10:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God's Judgment!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.99,0:10:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,El Thor!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.01,0:10:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.34,0:10:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aisa!! Pierre!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.17,0:11:17.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"God"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.34,0:11:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy... Aisa...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.67,0:11:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As tough as I am, that still hit me pretty hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.34,0:11:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That rubber thing... was quite annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.55,0:11:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However... this is the conclusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.06,0:11:46.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a large ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.73,0:11:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's the ark that the\NDivine Squad was forced to build.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.41,0:11:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, the northeast of the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.74,0:12:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After they get the gold, I'm meeting\Nup with them at this seashore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.51,0:12:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, as soon as everyone\Nshows up, you can leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.38,0:12:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If necessary, I can go once\Nthe treasure gets delivered.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.39,0:12:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N... Nami-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.39,0:12:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're coming to the seashore in the\Nnortheast... coming back to their ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.73,0:12:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go there and wait... for everyone to show.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.07,0:12:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I have to guide them to the Blue Sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.07,0:12:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the only one who can show them\Nthe way to escape the sky island!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.91,0:12:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to hurry to the Going Merry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.78,0:12:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had a long dream...\NYes, it was a dream about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.62,0:12:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Nami-san, you and I ate a forbidden\Nfruit and wandered in a paradise.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.13,0:12:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna wake up... Let us stay\Nforever in this beautiful dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.47,0:13:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Oh, Nami-san...\N--Hmmm... What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.08,0:13:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.58,0:13:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to stay in the dream with Nami-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.75,0:13:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm...? Nami-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.78,0:13:14.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Nami-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.62,0:13:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.25,0:13:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.13,0:13:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the hell is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.00,0:13:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mellorine... Mellorine, Mellorine...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.00,0:13:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mellorine, Mellorine,\NMellorine, Mellorine, Mello--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.47,0:13:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.81,0:13:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.61,0:13:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Wake up, Usopp!\NIt's no time to be in bed! Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.85,0:13:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it? Hm? What hap...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.19,0:13:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind that, just get ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.19,0:13:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? G-Get ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.20,0:14:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna rescue Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.53,0:14:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rescue? Res...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.10,0:14:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! Now I remember!\NGod! God appeared!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.52,0:14:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.02,0:14:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--God, God, God, God...\N--He isn't here anymore! He's long gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.86,0:14:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tremble, tremble, tremble,\Nfumble, fumble, fumble...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.53,0:14:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san was kidnapped by him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.03,0:14:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nami was?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.66,0:14:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! She was kidnapped\Nbecause we're so pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.20,0:14:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since she's cute...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.54,0:14:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, she was kidnapped?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.71,0:14:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.35,0:14:49.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.68,0:14:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.72,0:14:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?! A forest?! A ship?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.92,0:14:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though it was just for a\Nsecond, I saw her for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.02,0:15:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san is on that ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.53,0:15:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter what it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.63,0:15:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, she wasn't wearing her T-shirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.87,0:15:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That really doesn't matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.04,0:15:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get the situation at all. Where are\NConis, weird knight and the others?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.71,0:15:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know. Anyway, we have to hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.59,0:15:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where're we going, Sanji?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.26,0:15:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where else?! That ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.39,0:15:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.26,0:15:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we get any further behind,\Nwe won't be able to board!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.26,0:15:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now is our only chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.26,0:15:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, am I going, too,\Nby any chance? To that place?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.00,0:15:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!! You have that thing, right?!\NThe rope that you shoot out from your belly!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.00,0:15:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you mean "Usopp Aa-aa-aa"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.27,0:15:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll let you use this,\Nso I'll wait down here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.94,0:15:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Just hurry up!\N--I don't want to! W-Wait a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.95,0:15:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! There's no time to waste!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.95,0:16:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming for you!! Nami-san!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.93,0:16:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that the Ark Maxim has been activated,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.93,0:16:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even if they cry or scream, there is\Nno way for this nation to be saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.77,0:16:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sky island will fall from the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.27,0:16:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I, the Almighty God,\Nwill rise up to the land without end,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.94,0:16:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to the Endless Vearth...\Non the golden ark, Maxim.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.48,0:16:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. I shouldn't forget...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.65,0:16:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to pick up that treasure on my way up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.99,0:16:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The huge golden bell that\NShandora took pride in,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.33,0:16:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the grand belfry for that bell...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.83,0:16:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I needed to see the belfry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.67,0:16:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A golden bell...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.34,0:17:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A huge bell that's the most befitting\Nto me, who rules the heavens!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.34,0:17:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter? You're lucky\Nenough to have made it this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.95,0:17:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Abandon those who are incompetent.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.82,0:17:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must have a future you wish for, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.65,0:17:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A future I wish for...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.99,0:17:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.66,0:17:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if I just stay here and go with you,\Nit's the same as being alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.00,0:17:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get this party goin'! It's the\Nnight festival before gold-hunting!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.14,0:17:29.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get the treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.34,0:17:31.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Gold!\N--Gold!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.35,0:17:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the fun in gaining\Nwhat you want all by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.89,0:17:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There're actually a lot of things\NI want and that I'd like to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.39,0:17:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but if I have to abandon those\Nguys and go with you like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.06,0:17:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...then I don't want anything anymore!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.20,0:18:01.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't want anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.35,0:18:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That includes your life, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.18,0:18:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?! Hey, Suu?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.72,0:18:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both Usopp-san and Sanji-san\Naren't in shape to be moving around!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.16,0:18:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.77,0:18:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why aren't they here? Where are those two?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.67,0:18:33.80,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Um..."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.80,0:18:34.94,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Oh, yeah!"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.94,0:18:37.64,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"The guy with the cool\Neyebrows woke up first..."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.74,0:18:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji-san woke up...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.18,0:18:40.18,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"...and he woke up the\Ndubious guy with a long nose."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.21,0:18:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and woke Usopp-san up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.18,0:18:42.15,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"They ran very hard..."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.74,0:18:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And they both ran,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.45,0:18:43.45,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"...jumped using a weird gadget..."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.08,0:18:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and jumped... into the sky?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.45,0:18:44.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"...and went to that flying ship."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.75,0:18:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Don't tell me...!\NThey went to that ship?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.46,0:18:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their bodies still aren't...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.99,0:18:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How reckless!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.40,0:19:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are we really going to do it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.50,0:19:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are we really, seriously, going\Nto do it in this strong wind?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.41,0:19:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh... My "Can't Go to\NHigh Places" disease is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.41,0:19:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, I'll let you use this,\Nso go by yourse...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.41,0:19:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop rambling nonsense!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.12,0:19:28.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now!! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.96,0:19:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be responsible for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.47,0:19:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on... reach it!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.98,0:19:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not really a smart thing to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.48,0:19:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you've lost the means to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.52,0:19:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't want to be on this ship,\Nthen there is only one fate for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.52,0:20:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go to the afterlife.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.55,0:20:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh! I don't like this! Come off! Come off!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.85,0:20:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Shut up!\N--Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.85,0:20:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp! Don't swing, dummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.43,0:20:40.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.60,0:20:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp Aa... aa...! Hey...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.61,0:20:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God or not, if someone\Nlays a finger on Nami-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.28,0:21:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I will become a devil of the Blue Sea!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.92,0:21:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.93,0:21:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll put my all into this. Even if it\Ntakes all my energy and brainpower,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.77,0:21:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will survive!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.61,0:21:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One more time... Yes, to sail out to\Nsea with everyone one more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.16,0:21:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy... I'm gonna borrow your courage!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.17,0:21:59.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're feeling lonely, talk to me
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.68,0:22:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You gaze at the heavens\Nas you wander about
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.78,0:22:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like the moon,\Nyou keep your gaze constant
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.66,0:22:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And your deep reflection wanes\Nas you slowly disappear
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.84,0:22:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay as you are, let those words guide you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.02,0:22:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dream, you travelers who spend\Ncountless nights drifting
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.10,0:22:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you may not be able to go back
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.53,0:23:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you will surely start moving forward again
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.35,0:23:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you kidnap Nami-san?!\NBastard! You won't get away with this!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.15,0:23:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I stay here, I'll die for sure!\NI have to escape somehow!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.72,0:23:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no salvation for you at this point!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.56,0:23:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are we gonna do against God?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.22,0:23:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go... to the afterlife!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.56,0:23:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just hold on! I'll protect you\Neven if it costs me Usopp's life!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.23,0:23:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.23,0:23:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.56,0:23:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Two Awaken! On the Front Lines\Nof the Burning Love Rescue!!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.57,0:23:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.90,0:23:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
